
setValidator(QIntValidator(min, max, parent))
Description: Restricts the QLineEdit to accept only integer values within a specific range (e.g., -999 to 999). 
It prevents the user from entering letters or symbols that would break the logic.

setAlignment(Qt.AlignmentFlag)
Description: Controls the visual positioning of the text within the widget. In this case, it centers the number horizontally and vertically for better readability.
